109
00:05:12,494 --> 00:05:13,370
Clear sight.

110
00:05:14,912 --> 00:05:19,042
The power to see clearly
what's all around you.

111
00:05:19,042 --> 00:05:21,628
The Christ-like power of vision.

112
00:05:23,046 --> 00:05:27,050
The vision to penetrate the
mist and fog of deception

113
00:05:27,050 --> 00:05:30,262
