from his mist of concealment

117
00:05:42,732 --> 00:05:44,859
and put his claw
on your shoulder.

118
00:05:46,111 --> 00:05:47,445
Don't deny it.

119
00:05:48,613 --> 00:05:50,573
We all feel the
presence of evil.

120
00:05:52,784 --> 00:05:55,412
