1293
01:08:46,183 --> 01:08:47,725
- Yes.

1294
01:08:47,725 --> 01:08:49,352
- Nobody's trying to take
him away from you anymore?

1295
01:08:50,270 --> 01:08:51,063
- No.

1296
01:08:56,026 --> 01:08:58,070
- Because you're on
the path to recovery.

1297
01:08:59,404 --> 01:09:01,239
You're beginning
to remember things.

1298
01:09:02,865 --> 01:09:05,202
You've joined the
side of the angels.

1299
01:09:11,041 --> 01:09:14,502
- No matter what, Dr. Ofshe,
