utter miscarriage of justice

1304
01:09:30,685 --> 01:09:33,271
to prosecute Matthew Bradshaw

1305
01:09:33,271 --> 01:09:36,899
based on any confession he
gives in his current state.

1306
01:09:36,899 --> 01:09:41,071
Now that I would be
willing to testify to.

1307
01:09:42,155 --> 01:09:43,490
And I'd be very effective.

1308
01:09:44,907 --> 01:09:47,785
- Doctor, are you threatening
to go over to the defense?

1309
01:09:47,785 --> 01:09:49,329
- No, I work for you, Mr. Hart.

1310
01:09:50,497 --> 01:09:52,957
It's your responsibility
to do the right thing.

1311
01:09:54,501 --> 01:09:56,086
- Okay.

1312
01:09:56,086 --> 01:09:57,337
Send it to me in writing.

1313
01:10:02,467 --> 01:10:03,301
- You see this?

1314
01:10:03,301 --> 01:10:04,636
- What do you get?

1315
01:10:04,636 --> 01:10:06,679
- They found a college
kid who was missing.

1316
01:10:06,679 --> 01:10:08,931
