some devil worshiping cult

1317
01:10:08,931 --> 01:10:11,059
just across the
border in Mexico.

1318
01:10:11,059 --> 01:10:13,020
Lots of other burials too.

1319
01:10:13,020 --> 01:10:14,271
- Oh, God help us.

1320
01:10:15,647 --> 01:10:17,690
- At this time we
know little more

1321
01:10:17,690 --> 01:10:19,526
than what is public knowledge.

1322
01:10:19,526 --> 01:10:23,030
The bodies were recovered from
graves on a Mexican ranch.

1323
01:10:23,030 --> 01:10:24,989
The victims were killed
in a ritual manner

1324
01:10:24,989 --> 01:10:27,617
involving witchcraft and voodoo.

1325
01:10:27,617 --> 01:10:30,870
My department is in contact
with the Brownsville, Texas P.D.

1326
01:10:30,870 --> 01:10:32,872
- Is the Bradshaw cult
linked to Matamoros?

1327
01:10:32,872 --> 01:10:35,917
- There is increasing evidence
of a Satanic underground.

1328
01:10:35,917 --> 01:10:37,252
- Well, what about
Malcolm Norton's claim

1329
01:10:37,252 --> 01:10:38,878
that hundreds of
Satanic burial sites

1330
01:10:38,878 --> 01:10:40,130
will be found in this county?

1331
01:10:40,130 --> 01:10:41,631
- We're lucky enough to
have him working with us

1332
01:10:41,631 --> 01:10:42,924
on our search for these sights.

1333
01:10:42,924 --> 01:10:44,676
As you know, since
retiring from the FBI

1334
01:10:44,676 --> 01:10:46,553
