looking for evidence

1338
01:10:51,224 --> 01:10:52,809
of ritual burials.

1339
01:10:52,809 --> 01:10:54,644
Using the latest in
aerial search techniques,

1340
01:10:54,644 --> 01:10:57,397
we will try to pinpoint
their locations.

1341
01:10:57,397 --> 01:11:01,568
- Now for our part, we've
asked the state for $750,000

1342
01:11:01,568 --> 01:11:04,571
to buy helicopter mounted
infrared scanners.

1343
01:11:04,571 --> 01:11:06,489
We will locate these graves.

1344
01:11:08,366 --> 01:11:09,867
- [Ofshe Voiceover]
Dear Mr. Hart,

1345
01:11:10,952 --> 01:11:13,121
what follows is my
professional evaluation

1346
01:11:13,121 --> 01:11:15,790
of the Bradshaw cases
now before your office,

1347
01:11:17,250 --> 01:11:20,170
along with some background
materials from other writings.

1348
01:11:22,172 --> 01:11:25,425
Rebecca and Laura Bradshaw
are not credible witnesses.

1349
01:11:25,425 --> 01:11:28,345
There's no evidence to
confirm their allegations.

1350
01:11:28,345 --> 01:11:31,056
In addition, Laura's
allegations have nearly always

1351
01:11:31,056 --> 01:11:32,432
followed Rebecca's lead.

1352
01:11:33,766 --> 01:11:36,103
There's been so much
cross-talk between the victims

1353
01:11:36,103 --> 01:11:38,938
that we cannot know the actual
source of any allegation.

1354
01:11:40,315 --> 01:11:42,525
The invocation of
Satanic influence

1355
01:11:42,525 --> 01:11:44,611
is not unexpected here either.

1356
01:11:44,611 --> 01:11:47,739
When natural evidence to
support the charges is lacking,

1357
01:11:47,739 --> 01:11:50,908
one fall-back explanation
is that the supernatural

1358
01:11:50,908 --> 01:11:52,619
has made it so.

1359
01:11:52,619 --> 01:11:55,413
Especially in an environment
so highly charged

1360
01:11:55,413 --> 01:11:56,664
with religious fervor.

1361
01:11:58,708 --> 01:12:01,211
The brainwashing methods
used on Matt by the police

1362
01:12:01,211 --> 01:12:03,880
are more common than
generally believed.

1363
01:12:03,880 --> 01:12:07,050
And the longer he is made to
repeat these false memories,

1364
01:12:07,050 --> 01:12:09,761
the more he himself will
believe that they are true.

1365
01:12:11,638 --> 01:12:13,640
Three hundred years
ago in Massachusetts,

1366
01:12:13,640 --> 01:12:16,226
there was an outcry
against Satanism.

1367
01:12:16,226 --> 01:12:20,772
In that time, the accused
were old, poor, outcast women.

1368
01:12:20,772 --> 01:12:24,442
And the men who judged them
were powerful and successful.

1369
01:12:24,442 --> 01:12:27,987
Today's accusers are often
young middle-class women.

1370
01:12:27,987 --> 01:12:31,158
The accused are often the most
powerful and successful men

1371
01:12:31,158 --> 01:12:32,784
of the community.

1372
01:12:32,784 --> 01:12:35,203
The players have changed places,

1373
01:12:35,203 --> 01:12:39,207
but the potential for frenzy
and injustice remains the same.

1374
01:12:39,207 --> 01:12:42,835
In Salem then or
in Clarkwell today.

1375
01:12:45,172 --> 01:12:47,840
(phone ringing)

1376
01:12:49,634 --> 01:12:50,427
- Hart.

1377
01:12:53,055 --> 01:12:55,057
Yes, Doctor, I read
it this afternoon.

1378
01:12:56,599 --> 01:12:57,809
Thank you for your efforts

1379
01:12:57,809 --> 01:12:59,644
but we're pressing
forward with Bradshaw.

1380
01:12:59,644 --> 01:13:00,812
- You're going ahead?

1381
