but the printer just
used reply boxes,

1390
01:13:35,847 --> 01:13:38,016
yes, no, no opinion.
(students laughing)

1391
01:13:38,016 --> 01:13:40,018
- Dr. Ofshe?
- Yes, sir.

1392
01:13:40,018 --> 01:13:41,228
- I'm Horton Leggett.

1393
01:13:41,228 --> 01:13:43,605
I represent Everett and
Sweetzer in Clarkwell.

1394
01:13:45,732 --> 01:13:46,858
- Could you excuse us?

1395
01:13:48,901 --> 01:13:50,528
- Doctor, there are
two innocent men

1396
01:13:50,528 --> 01:13:52,364
