1402
01:14:04,167 --> 01:14:06,253
when she said her attackers
were friends of her father,

1403
01:14:06,253 --> 01:14:08,171
so when they showed
her pictures of men,

1404
01:14:08,171 --> 01:14:10,340
she just picked out
faces she already knew.

1405
01:14:11,716 --> 01:14:14,302
And as for Wayne's polygraph,
that was a nightmare.

1406
01:14:14,302 --> 01:14:16,388
