1410
01:14:22,102 --> 01:14:24,604
questions the girls' veracity
and Matt's confessions.

1411
01:14:24,604 --> 01:14:27,190
- I'm not at liberty
to discuss my report.

1412
01:14:27,190 --> 01:14:28,733
- But if you're convinced

1413
01:14:28,733 --> 01:14:30,235
that Matt's confessions were
made under duress, surely--

1414
01:14:30,235 --> 01:14:34,822
- Look, please, don't
put words in my mouth.

1415
01:14:36,033 --> 01:14:38,201
I'm in a very tricky
ethical position here.

1416
01:14:39,411 --> 01:14:40,870
I was hired by the
District Attorney.

1417
01:14:40,870 --> 01:14:44,957
I can't just turn my
findings over to the defense.

1418
01:14:44,957 --> 01:14:46,584
The judge has to do that.

1419
01:14:46,584 --> 01:14:48,170
- See, that's part
of the problem.

1420
01:14:48,170 --> 01:14:50,797
I'm not sure the judge knows
your report even exists.

1421
01:14:52,465 --> 01:14:54,467
- Well, that's not right.

1422
01:14:54,467 --> 01:14:57,304
- No, no, just have
everybody stand in place.

1423
01:14:57,304 --> 01:14:59,306
This recess won't
take but a minute.

1424
01:14:59,306 --> 01:15:00,515
- Good morning, Your Honor.

1425
01:15:00,515 --> 01:15:02,350
- I received this
from a Doctor Ofshe,

1426
01:15:02,350 --> 01:15:03,601
