1427
01:15:03,601 --> 01:15:05,853
- Yes, Dr. Ofshe was
employed by my office.

1428
01:15:05,853 --> 01:15:08,315
- Why wasn't this report
included in discovery?

1429
01:15:08,315 --> 01:15:10,525
- Well, it's not evidence,
it's only his opinion.

1430
01:15:10,525 --> 01:15:12,235
- But it's an important
expert opinion,

1431
01:15:12,235 --> 01:15:14,321
which all the defendants
should be aware of.

1432
01:15:14,321 --> 01:15:15,238
- Your Honor...

1433
01:15:15,238 --> 01:15:17,615
- Distribute it, immediately.

1434
01:15:18,616 --> 01:15:19,451
- Yes, sir.

1435
01:15:27,417 --> 01:15:31,463
- Gentlemen, I've just read
the most interesting report.

1436
01:15:31,463 --> 01:15:33,381
Look at the second
page, top paragraph.

1437
01:15:38,761 --> 01:15:40,763
- This says the girls are lying.

1438
01:15:40,763 --> 01:15:42,265
- That's right.

1439
01:15:42,265 --> 01:15:44,267
- You mean, we're not the
only ones saying it anymore.

1440
01:15:44,267 --> 01:15:45,560
- That's right.

1441
01:15:45,560 --> 01:15:46,894
The D.A.'s office is
trying to reach me.

1442
01:15:48,855 --> 01:15:50,440
- You think they're
gonna make us an offer?

1443
01:15:50,440 --> 01:15:52,567
- I wouldn't be surprised.

1444
01:15:52,567 --> 01:15:55,570
Plead to some
misdemeanor, credit for
time served, you walk.

1445
01:15:56,779 --> 01:15:58,323
- I ain't pleading
guilty to nothing.

1446
01:15:58,323 --> 01:15:59,366
I didn't do nothing.

1447
01:16:04,787 --> 01:16:06,248
- He's right.

1448
01:16:06,248 --> 01:16:07,082
No deal.

1449
01:16:10,293 --> 01:16:13,588
- Tim, please, we've got
to stick to basic evidence.

1450
