crisscrossed this entire county,

1457
01:16:27,685 --> 01:16:30,522
didn't find a single
Satanic burial site.

1458
01:16:30,522 --> 01:16:32,107
Meanwhile, back here on Earth,

1459
01:16:32,107 --> 01:16:33,566
the good citizens
are beginning to ask

1460
01:16:33,566 --> 01:16:36,694
why we haven't prosecuted
anyone in this case.

1461
01:16:36,694 --> 01:16:38,405
- Well, we can't go to trial.

1462
01:16:38,405 --> 01:16:41,449
Not with what we got on Wayne
Everett and Steve Sweetzer.

1463
01:16:41,449 --> 01:16:42,825
- Offer them a deal.

1464
01:16:42,825 --> 01:16:44,536
- I offered, they said no.

1465
01:16:44,536 --> 01:16:46,579
- Well, we got
Matt's confession.

1466
01:16:46,579 --> 01:16:48,706
I'm pretty sure he'll
repeat for the judge.

1467
01:16:51,834 --> 01:16:54,504
(phone ringing)

1468
01:16:55,380 --> 01:16:56,673
- It's got to be Bradshaw.

1469
01:17:00,635 --> 01:17:02,304
- Hart, did you cut
a deal with the D.A.?

1470
01:17:02,304 --> 01:17:04,597
- The D.A.'s dropped all
charges against my clients.

1471
01:17:04,597 --> 01:17:06,016
They're free men.

1472
01:17:06,016 --> 01:17:07,809
We have no further statements
to make at this time.

1473
01:17:07,809 --> 01:17:08,935
- Wayne, Steve.

1474
01:17:10,145 --> 01:17:11,604
