1476
01:17:12,814 --> 01:17:14,649
- Too angry to say anything.

1477
01:17:14,649 --> 01:17:18,153
- You've been a good soldier
against Satan up to now.

1478
01:17:18,153 --> 01:17:20,988
Despite his snares
and deceptions,

1479
01:17:20,988 --> 01:17:24,117
you have seen the truth of
the past and spoken it aloud.

1480
01:17:26,578 --> 01:17:28,246
- I have tried.

1481
01:17:28,246 --> 01:17:29,039
- I know.

1482
01:17:31,374 --> 01:17:34,252
But sometimes soldiers
receive wounds,

1483
01:17:34,252 --> 01:17:36,671
noble wounds won in battle.

1484
01:17:38,631 --> 01:17:42,177
This is your time, Matt,
to receive chastisement.

1485
01:17:44,887 --> 01:17:46,389
- God's chastisement?

1486
01:17:46,389 --> 01:17:47,807
- Oh, no.

1487
01:17:47,807 --> 01:17:49,684
Nothing so terrible.

1488
01:17:49,684 --> 01:17:52,687
I mean chastisement
under man's law.

1489
01:17:54,856 --> 01:17:56,441
- Yeah, but Reverend,

1490
01:17:58,443 --> 01:18:02,780
now I heard, you know,
guys in jail talk and,

1491
01:18:04,241 --> 01:18:08,661
that Dr. Ofshe, he thinks I
didn't do any of these things,

1492
01:18:11,289 --> 01:18:12,832
that my girls have been lying.

1493
01:18:16,711 --> 01:18:17,837
- Do you believe that?

1494
01:18:22,884 --> 01:18:23,718
- No.

1495
01:18:25,387 --> 01:18:27,055
I don't see how
it could be true.

1496
01:18:29,099 --> 01:18:30,058
But--

1497
01:18:30,058 --> 01:18:32,060
- Don't be misled.

1498
01:18:33,228 --> 01:18:35,813
Godless science loves a mystery,

1499
01:18:35,813 --> 01:18:39,151
because it believes
this universe is unknown

1500
01:18:39,151 --> 01:18:41,278
and always changing.

1501
01:18:41,278 --> 01:18:43,321
But not you and I, Matthew.

1502
01:18:43,321 --> 01:18:45,657
For we know God's Love.

1503
01:18:45,657 --> 01:18:48,118
And that Love is our universe.

1504
01:18:48,118 --> 01:18:49,619
There are no mysteries for us.

1505
01:18:53,873 --> 01:18:54,749
- Yeah.

1506
01:18:57,002 --> 01:18:57,835
Yeah.

1507
01:18:59,671 --> 01:19:01,423
I just want this to
be over, you know.

1508
